data.description: You have the opportunity to own your own land which means this manufactured home is financeable!  Situated in an active 55+ community in Central Naples. Tucked away at the end of a cul-de-sac on a lake view lot, privacy is ensured in this tranquil setting. Step inside to discover a meticulously maintained interior that boasts numerous upgrades and modern finishes. The HVAC system and entire plumbing system were replaced only 3 short years ago. The interior features new laminate flooring and brand new floorboards, creating a fresh and inviting atmosphere. The updated kitchen showcases hard surface counters, new cabinets, and newer appliances. Enjoy the outdoors in the expansive screened patio that wraps around behind the home overlooking the lake, offering ample space for relaxation and entertaining. Additionally, a separate utility/workshop room with a washer/dryer provides convenience and functionality. Don't miss out on this remarkable opportunity to own a property that combines affordability, stunning lake views, and the convenience of a central Naples location.
